snippet.title: Love Bites - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.winterwolves.com/lovebites.htm
The official trailer of Love Bites, my new dating sim. Play as Kaitlyn or Brandon and romance Sabrina, Viktor, Tyrone and Nadia.
Discover your sickness' origins and find a cure before it's too late!
